Hardware Requirements
•	Raspberry Pi 3 Model B+
•	8Gb Micro SD Card
•	Screen\Display
•	Raspberry Pi Camera Module v2
•	Dexter GrovePi Board
•	Grove – Sound Sensor
•	Grove – Ultrasonic Sensor
•	Grove – LCD Display
•	Grove – Red LED
•	Grove – Blue LED
•	Grove – Green LED
•	Sensor Cables

Software Requirements
•	Raspbian OS
•	SSH Client (PuTTY)
•	Python 2.7
•	Node-RED v0.18.4
•	Node-Red Dashboard version 2.9.1
•	Node.js v9.11.1

Scripting Languages
•	Python
•	JavaScript
•	JSON
•	HTML
•	Python 2.7
